    <section>
        <title>wrapper.java.mainclass</title>
        <para>
            Class to execute when the wrapper starts the application.  The
            value of this property depends on which of the integration methods
            that were selected.  In most cases this is NOT the main class of
            your application.
        </para>
        <informalexample>
            <simpara><emphasis>Example (WrapperSimpleApp integration method):</emphasis></simpara>
            <screen format="linespecific"><![CDATA[wrapper.java.mainclass=org.tanukisoftware.wrapper.WrapperSimpleApp]]></screen>
        </informalexample>
    </section>
